# Plantilla: Harness State JSON

> Fase: Features (transversal)
> Artefacto: `.harness-state.json`

---

{
  "project": "{Nombre del Proyecto}",
  "createdAt": "{ISO8601}",
  "updatedAt": "{ISO8601}",
  "humanInTheLoop": true,
  "inception": {
    "status": "pending",
    "approved": false
  },
  "features": []
}

---

## Schema completo (con features y HUs pobladas)

```jsonc
{
  "project": "OrderService",
  "createdAt": "2026-05-26T00:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2026-05-26T00:00:00Z",
  "humanInTheLoop": true,

  // Inception: pre-fase de proyecto, se ejecuta UNA sola vez
  "inception": {
    "status": "completed",        // pending | in_progress | completed
    "approved": true,             // HITL obligatorio
    "startedAt": "2026-05-26T00:00:00Z",
    "completedAt": "2026-05-26T04:00:00Z"
  },

  "features": [
    {
      "id": "F001",                          // Auto-incrementado
      "name": "Registro de usuarios con OAuth2",
      "slug": "registro-usuarios-oauth2",    // kebab-case
      "description": "Implementar flujo de registro con Google y Microsoft",
      "status": "in_progress",               // pending | in_progress | in_review | done | blocked
      "assignedTo": null,
      "docsPath": "docs/features/F001-registro-usuarios-oauth2/",
      "branch": "feature/F001-registro-usuarios-oauth2",
      "prUrl": null,                         // URL del PR feature → develop
      "createdAt": "2026-05-26T00:00:00Z",
      "startedAt": "2026-05-26T02:00:00Z",
      "completedAt": null,

      // Fases feature-level (2 fases)
      "phases": {
        "analysis": {
          "status": "completed",             // pending | in_progress | completed | blocked
          "approved": true,                  // HITL
          "startedAt": "2026-05-26T02:00:00Z",
          "completedAt": "2026-05-26T03:00:00Z"
        },
        "design": {
          "status": "completed",
          "approved": true,
          "startedAt": "2026-05-26T03:00:00Z",
          "completedAt": "2026-05-26T04:00:00Z"
        }
      },

      // Historias de usuario (registradas tras analysis)
      "userStories": [
        {
          "id": "US-001",                    // Auto-incrementado dentro de la feature
          "title": "Registro con Google OAuth2",
          "status": "in_progress",           // pending | in_progress | in_review | done | blocked
          "branch": "hu/F001-US-001-registro-google-oauth2",
          "prUrl": null,                     // URL del PR hu/* → feature/*
          "docsPath": "docs/features/F001-registro-usuarios-oauth2/US-001/",

          // Fases HU-level (4 fases)
          "phases": {
            "develop": {
              "status": "in_progress",
              "approved": false,
              "startedAt": "2026-05-26T04:00:00Z",
              "completedAt": null
            },
            "test": {
              "status": "pending",
              "approved": false
            },
            "quality": {
              "status": "pending",
              "approved": false
            },
            "deploy": {
              "status": "pending",
              "approved": false
            }
          },

          // TDD tracking por HU
          "tdd": {
            "step": "red",                   // red | green | refactor
            "class": "GoogleOAuthHandler",
            "method": "HandleAsync",
            "testFile": "tests/OrderService.UnitTests/Application/Auth/GoogleOAuthHandlerTests/HandleAsyncTests.cs",
            "scenario": "Should_ReturnToken_When_GoogleCodeIsValid",
            "scenariosCompleted": ["Should_ReturnToken_When_GoogleCodeIsValid"],
            "scenariosPending": [
              "Should_ReturnError_When_GoogleCodeIsInvalid",
              "Should_ReturnError_When_GoogleApiUnavailable"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "US-002",
          "title": "Registro con Microsoft OAuth2",
          "status": "pending",
          "branch": null,
          "prUrl": null,
          "docsPath": "docs/features/F001-registro-usuarios-oauth2/US-002/",
          "phases": {
            "develop": { "status": "pending", "approved": false },
            "test":    { "status": "pending", "approved": false },
            "quality": { "status": "pending", "approved": false },
            "deploy":  { "status": "pending", "approved": false }
          },
          "tdd": null
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

## Estados validos

### Inception

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `inception.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed` |
| `inception.approved` | `true`, `false` |

### Feature

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `features[].status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `in_review`, `done`, `blocked` |
| `features[].phases.{fase}.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `blocked` |
| `features[].phases.{fase}.approved` | `true`, `false` |

### HU

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `userStories[].status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `in_review`, `done`, `blocked` |
| `userStories[].phases.{fase}.status` | `pending`, `in_progress`, `completed`, `blocked` |
| `userStories[].phases.{fase}.approved` | `true`, `false` |

### TDD

| Campo | Valores |
|-------|---------|
| `tdd.step` | `red`, `green`, `refactor` |
